snippet.title: Dolls Run Away from Diana
snippet.description:
Diana has a lot of dolls and she treats them carelessly. Dolls offended and fled from Diana. The video will let the children know that they need to love and take care of their toys.
Diana's INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
